OL,3,CBadger baiter who kept dogs in
OL,4,C'appalling' conditions sentenced
OL,6,FA man who trained his dogs to fight
OL,7,Fbadgers "for entertainment" has been
OL,8,Fgiven a suspended prison sentence.
OL,10,FLeeds Magistrates Court heard
OL,11,FMackenzie Ward, 21, had four dogs
OL,12,Fwhich were found living in "appalling"
OL,13,Fconditions with untreated injuries
OL,14,Fcaused by badger baiting.
OL,16,FThe illegal bloodsport sees dogs being
OL,17,Fsent into setts to attack badgers.
