OL,3,CBadger baiter who kept dogs in
OL,4,C'appalling' conditions sentenced
OL,6,FWard was arrested after police and the
OL,7,FRSPCA executed a warrant at an address
OL,8,Fin Seacroft, Leeds, in March. The
OL,9,Fdogs, one of which which was covered
OL,10,Fin ticks and suffering from untreated
OL,11,Fpuncture wounds, were seized.
OL,13,FWard, of Moresdale Lane, Leeds,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to causing unnecessary
OL,15,Fsuffering to a protected animal,
OL,16,Fcausing an animal to fight and failing
OL,17,Fto ensure the welfare of an animal.
