OL,3,CBadger baiter who kept dogs in
OL,4,C'appalling' conditions sentenced
OL,6,FHe was was given a 26-week custodial
OL,7,Fsentence, suspended for 12 months, and
OL,8,Fa five-day rehabilitation order, with
OL,9,F200 hours of unpaid work and a 10-year
OL,10,Fban on keeping animals.
OL,12,FSgt Andy Katkowski, who led the
OL,13,Finvestigation, said: "The conditions
OL,14,Fthese four dogs were found being kept
OL,15,Fin were truly appalling and we believe
OL,16,Fthe injuries to one of the dogs was
OL,17,Fthe result of it being involved in
OL,18,Fanimal fighting, most likely with a
OL,19,Fbadger.
