OL,3,CBadger baiter who kept dogs in
OL,4,C'appalling' conditions sentenced
OL,6,F"Badger-related offences are a
OL,7,Fparticularly cruel form of wildlife
OL,8,Fcrime where badgers face a horrific
OL,9,Fand prolonged death purely for the
OL,10,Fentertainment of those involved.
OL,12,F"It is an illegal activity that is
OL,13,Foften linked to other types of crime
OL,14,Fand the police and our partner
OL,15,Fagencies will continue to target those
OL,16,Fwho take part in this so-called
OL,17,Fbloodsport."
